data.description: Cream puff ranch with all-new quality appointments. Yes! builder grade features replaced with  3/4" hardwood, tile flooring, soft-close city-scape cabinets, pot drawers, interior paint, 3 cm "Carolina Summer" grade 5 granite counters, high quality SS appliances, full-tile backsplash, huge island w deep SS sink, brushed nickel hardware, lighting, floor-to-ceiling corner gas fireplace design.  You'll love the light & bright open feel. 10' ceilings. Relax under your new Sunsetter auto shade with all new landscaping trees & plants in the manicured lot backing to open space. Sprinkler system has irrigation water. Great for entertaining or just privacy. New class 4 roof, 3-car garage. Huge unfinished basement. Pride in ownership. Blue Ribbon Home warranty for buyers. Possible closing cost help
